Atayım kendimi, gebereyim.

137
00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İki kere denedim. Yapamadım.

138
00:08:50.920 --> 00:08:52.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Köye dönen virajda durdum.

139
00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:57.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Götürüp manzaraya baktırırdın ya
hani bize.

140
00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Durdum orada.

141
00:09:01.640 --> 00:09:04.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çektim arabayı. Aşağı baktım.

142
00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:08.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dedim, bırakayım kendimi.

143
00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir düğünün sesi geldi uzaktan.

144
00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çenem titredi.

145
00:09:17.520 --> 00:09:18.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tarık burun çeker]

146
00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:22.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sanki kalbimin içinde titriyordu çenem.

147
00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:24.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[burun çeker]

148
00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:32.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Evlendiğim gün,</i>
<i>o gece bana söylediğin şey geldi aklıma.</i>

149
00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:35.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tarık nefes alır]

150
00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:39.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Biz arabaya binerken</i>
<i>çektin ya beni kenara, hatırlıyor musun?</i>

151
00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:41.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Sigara vardı benim ağzımda.</i>

152
00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:44.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Sen şöyle iki parmağınla,</i>
<i>çektin sigarayı dudaklarımdan.</i>

153
00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:47.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Bir nefes aldın,</i>
<i>yere attın, hatırlıyor musun?</i>

154
00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:50.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[fonda dramatik müzik]

155
00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:55.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>"Ne bok yersen ye,</i>

156
00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:57.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>yatağa küs girme," dedin bana.</i>

157
00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:00.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Hatırlıyor musun baba?</i>

158
00:10:04.400 --> 00:10:05.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O geldi aklıma.

159
00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hakkımı helal etmiyorum.

160
00:10:20.920 --> 00:10:22.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana da abine de!

161
00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:24.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[ağlayarak] Öldü baba. Öldü.

162
00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:25.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben öldürdüm!

163
00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:27.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oğlun. Ben!

164
00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:30.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben sevdiğim kadını öldürdüm!

165
00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:34.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[müzik devam ediyor]

166
00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:49.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sağ ol.

167
00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:57.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[burun çeker] Senin mi bu?

168
00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:01.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dramatik müzik]

169
00:11:06.640 --> 00:11:07.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne ki o?

170
00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:10.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Senin mi, değil mi?

171
00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:24.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne zaman gördün en son onu?

172
00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:27.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kimi?

173
00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:30.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kardeşini.

174
00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:35.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bilmem, hatırlamıyorum.

175
00:11:35.880 --> 00:11:37.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oldu epey.

176
00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:40.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hatırla, lütfen.

177
00:11:43.240 --> 00:11:45.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben gitmeden önce mi, sonra mı? Ne zaman?

178
00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:48.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefesle güler]

179
00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen yokken işte... Sen...

180
00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:58.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yoktun, tabii...

181
00:11:58.080 --> 00:12:00.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[derin nefes] Birkaç hafta, öyle bir şey.

182
00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:06.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Babamlardayım dedi bana.
Ben yokken hep oradaymış.

183
00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:08.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oraya mı gittin sen de? Orada mı gördün?

184
00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefesle güler]

185
00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:17.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne oluyor ya?

186
00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:19.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorguya mı çekiyorsun beni?

187
00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:22.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye yalan söyledin bana?

188
00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:25.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kapıdan girer girmez kaldırdım seni dedin.

189
00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:29.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sigaran sönüyordu, neredeyse,
niye yalan söyledin?

190
00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:32.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Girdiğimde sigara ağzımdaydı.
Sonra gittim oraya koydum. Seni kaldırdım.

191
00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ne oluyor? Niye böyle yapıyorsun?
Ne yap...

192
00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye, yani...

193
00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:37.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne var bunda? Ben...

194
00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:40.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sadece buraya bir uğradım. Hepsi bu!

195
00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:45.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Acayip acayip laflar, garip garip haller.
Ne oluyorsun Allah aşkına ya?

196
00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:48.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hadi kalk, bir hastaneye gidelim.
Bir şey yapalım. Kardeşim nerede?

197
00:12:49.760 --> 00:12:51.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Söyledim sana. Duymadın mı?

198
00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:52.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne?

199
00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:55.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kardeşin beni öldürmeye çalıştı!

200
00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:57.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sonra da çekip gitti.

201
00:12:58.760 --> 00:13:01.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sonra da seni yolladı belki.
Nereden belli?

202
00:13:01.320 --> 00:13:04.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ya niye yapsın böyle bir şeyi?
Niye öldürmek istesin seni kardeşim?

203
00:13:04.520 --> 00:13:07.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Köpek gibi özledi çocuk seni.
Kaç gün burada gün saydı!

204
00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:09.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne zamandır yoksun.

205
00:13:09.520 --> 00:13:11.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Kusura bakma ama anlamıyorum.
Kafam basmıyor.

206
00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:14.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Domuz gibi içmişsin yine.
Leş gibi kokuyorsun.

207
00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:17.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aç kulağını, beni dinle.

208
00:13:19.280 --> 00:13:22.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Gidip bulacağız senin kardeşini.
Polise götüreceğiz.

209
00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:24.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Birini öldürdü senin kardeşin.

210
00:13:27.680 --> 00:13:29.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Nermin nefes verir]

211
00:13:36.640 --> 00:13:37.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Nermin nefes verir]

212
00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:42.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İyi misin anne?

213
00:13:44.840 --> 00:13:46.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yaptık biz sana?

214
00:13:47.600 --> 00:13:48.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ha?

215
00:13:48.760 --> 00:13:50.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Neyi yanlış yaptık oğlum?

216
00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:52.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Neyi eksik yaptık?

217
00:13:54.120 --> 00:13:56.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Baban titriyor içeride.

218
00:13:57.480 --> 00:13:59.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne konuştun? Ne söyledin?

219
00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:02.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne konuştun da tir tir titriyor adam?

220
00:14:03.520 --> 00:14:05.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yuttun mu anne sen hapını?

221
00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Babam yutsun dedi bak.

222
00:14:07.880 --> 00:14:10.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yuttuk hapı biz oğlum. Yuttuk.

223
00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:13.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Allah senden razı olsun.
Sayende hapı yuttuk.

224
00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:16.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bittim, tükendim ben be!

225
00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:18.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Valla, geberip gitsem diye dua ediyorum.

226
00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:20.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Deme anne şöyle şeyler ya.

227
00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:22.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Abin de başka türlü.

228
00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:27.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İyice aynısı. Nasıl şeyse?

229
00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:29.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kopyası olmuş artık o babanın.

230
00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:32.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aynı dalda iki kuru armutlar sanki.

231
00:14:32.720 --> 00:14:36.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oğlum konuş. Bin defa söyledim, konuşmaz.

232
00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:38.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Oğlum niye gitti karın evden?" dedim.

233
00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Olur böyle şeyler," dedim.

234
00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:42.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evlilik zor iş. Yürütmek zor.

235
00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:45.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anlaşmak zor. Konuşun. Konuş.

236
00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:49.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yok. Öyle domuz gibi bakar
insanın suratına.

237
00:14:50.360 --> 00:14:51.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gece sesleri]

238
00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Anne, karışma."

239
00:14:53.800 --> 00:14:56.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İyi, karışmadık işte. Karışmadık. Ne oldu?

240
00:14:59.640 --> 00:15:00.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bana bak.

241
00:15:02.040 --> 00:15:04.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hakikaten dövüyor muydu abin karısını?

242
00:15:04.840 --> 00:15:08.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bir kere evlerine gittik de
Rüya'nın gözü mosmordu.

243
00:15:09.880 --> 00:15:12.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bak, ölümü öp. Böyle bir şey varsa söyle.

244
00:15:12.680 --> 00:15:14.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Saklanmaz. Anneden babadan saklanmaz.

245
00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:17.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-O kızın da bir ailesi var. İnsanlar...
-Bilmiyorum anne.

246
00:15:19.440 --> 00:15:21.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dövmüyordur herhalde, niye dövsün?

247
00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:24.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne bileyim? İçine atıp atıp...

248
00:15:24.920 --> 00:15:28.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bak, böyle bir şey varsa
ölümü öp diyorum. Söyle.

249
00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:32.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İçki içiyor mu?

250
00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:33.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bilmiyorum anne.

251
00:15:33.720 --> 00:15:35.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Soru sorup durma, sıkma insanı.
Bilmiyorum.

252
00:15:35.960 --> 00:15:37.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tersleme beni! Tersleme!

253
00:15:39.160 --> 00:15:40.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Saygısız köpek!

254
00:15:40.960 --> 00:15:43.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Kuyruğun sıkışınca dönüp gelmeyi
biliyorsun ama.

255
00:15:44.480 --> 00:15:47.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Pabuç gibi dil.
Utanmadan azarlıyor insanı.

256
00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:50.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ay köpek doğurmuşum ben be, köpek!

257
00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:54.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Koy mama tasını önüne.
Yalasın, yutsun, kapsın kolunu.

258
00:15:54.560 --> 00:15:56.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ömür törpüsü müsünüz siz be?

259
00:15:56.680 --> 00:15:59.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Zehir ettiniz bana hayatı. Zehir!

260
00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:07.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Git içeride setin üstünde yufka var çiğ.

261
00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:08.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Isıt, ye.

262
00:16:08.560 --> 00:16:10.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sabah olacak, bir şey yemedin daha.

263
00:16:12.360 --> 00:16:14.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ağabeyine diye yapmıştım.

264
00:16:16.280 --> 00:16:18.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kaç oldu saat? Nerede kaldı bu çocuk?

265
00:16:20.760 --> 00:16:22.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Nermin nefes alır]

266
00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:32.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye öldürmek istesin seni kardeşim?

267
00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:34.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bulup ona sorsana.

268
00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:38.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye böyle bir şey yapmak istesin?

269
00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:40.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen niye dövüyordun karını?

270
00:16:41.240 --> 00:16:44.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Karımı dövmüyorum. Bilip bilmeden
başkasının işine burnunu sokma.

271
00:16:44.520 --> 00:16:47.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[nefesle güler] Ya, moda değil mi
o gözlükler öyle?

272
00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:50.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir konu mu var aranızda?

273
00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:52.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tartıştınız mı, bir şey mi var?

274
00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:54.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye öldürmek istesin seni bu çocuk?

275
00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bilmem.

276
00:16:56.960 --> 00:16:58.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok seviyordu, ondan belki.

277
00:16:58.760 --> 00:17:00.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seviyordu tabii.

278
00:17:01.800 --> 00:17:03.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şüphen mi var sevgisinden?

279
00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:07.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yok. Ne önemi var ki?

280
00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:09.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen de Rüya'yı çok seviyorsun belki.

281
00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:12.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Karıştırmasana Rüya'yı. Konuşma.

282
00:17:12.680 --> 00:17:14.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana ne ya benim karımdan?

283
00:17:14.600 --> 00:17:16.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kardeşimi soruyorum ben sana.

284
00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:18.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Senin kardeşin hasta.

285
00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:21.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hepiniz biliyorsunuz.

286
00:17:21.240 --> 00:17:23.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bal gibi biliyorsunuz.
Hiçbir şey yapmıyorsunuz.

287
00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:25.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne sen, ne anan, ne baban.

288
00:17:25.480 --> 00:17:26.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yavaş!

289
00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:30.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kalk.

290
00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:32.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kalk gidip bulacağız kardeşini.

291
00:17:33.880 --> 00:17:35.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Otur.
-Kalk!

292
00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:38.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Otur.
-Kalk dedim, gideceğiz!

293
00:17:38.320 --> 00:17:39.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Otur lan oraya! Otur!

294
00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:41.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[bağırarak] Otur!

295
00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:46.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ben karıma parmağımın ucuyla
bile vurmadım. Elimi sürmedim.

296
00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:50.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner burnundan soluyor]

297
00:17:54.360 --> 00:17:55.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dramatik müzik]

298
00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:11.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[müzik devam ediyor]

299
00:18:18.280 --> 00:18:21.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner nefes nefese]

300
00:18:21.320 --> 00:18:22.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rüya?

301
00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:26.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rüya, dur.

302
00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:29.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rüya?

303
00:18:30.280 --> 00:18:33.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ne işin var senin burada?
Beni mi takip ettin?

304
00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Niye yaptın böyle bir şeyi Taner?

305
00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:37.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Taner, dur yalvarırım!
-Bırak!

306
00:18:37.520 --> 00:18:39.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Taner bir dur, bir dinle beni.

307
00:18:39.760 --> 00:18:41.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bak, daha fazla zorlaştırma.

308
00:18:41.320 --> 00:18:42.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seninle baştan konuştuk.

309
00:18:42.800 --> 00:18:44.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anlaştık. Kabul ettin.

310
00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:45.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Yapma böyle.
-Bırak, Rüya!

311
00:18:46.160 --> 00:18:48.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bana bak! Bana bak! Yüzüme bak!

312
00:18:49.280 --> 00:18:52.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Eğer o kapıyı çalarsan bir daha
beni göremezsin, anladın mı?

313
00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:53.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şu haline bak!

314
00:18:53.680 --> 00:18:55.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu nasıl manyaklık lan?

315
00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:57.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ha? Bu nasıl manyaklık!

316
00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:58.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nasıl izin verirsin böyle bir şeye?

317
00:18:59.080 --> 00:19:01.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya... Duyuyor musun sen beni Taner?

318
00:19:01.480 --> 00:19:03.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Görmek istiyorum, tanımak istiyorum
o şerefsizi!

319
00:19:04.520 --> 00:19:07.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ölmüş anamın üstüne yeminle,
çeker, giderim Taner.

320
00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:10.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seninle bir anlaşma yaptık.

321
00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:13.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bak, şu yüzüğü parmağıma daha
takmadan biliyordun her şeyi.

322
00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:15.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hiçbir şeyi saklamadım senden.

323
00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İstemiyorsan, ayıralım yollarımızı dedim.

324
00:19:18.040 --> 00:19:21.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Olmaz, dedin. Sensiz yapamam, dedin.
Razıyım, dedim.

325
00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:22.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Söz verdin bana.

326
00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Git, çal o kapıyı.

327
00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İstediğin buysa git, çal o kapıyı.

328
00:19:28.160 --> 00:19:29.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama beni de unut.

329
00:19:30.160 --> 00:19:31.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rüya?

330
00:19:32.120 --> 00:19:34.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefes verir] Ya çal o kapıyı...

331
00:19:35.240 --> 00:19:38.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
...ya da verdiğin sözü tut.
Gel, evimize gidelim.

332
00:19:40.920 --> 00:19:43.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dramatik müzik]

333
00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:48.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi, karar ver. Durmayalım burada.

334
00:19:54.880 --> 00:19:56.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner] <i>Aşığı dövdü onu.</i>

335
00:19:57.760 --> 00:19:59.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>O şerefsiz.</i>

336
00:19:59.360 --> 00:20:00.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Kimse bilmez.</i>

337
00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:05.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Annem, babam, kardeşim, kimse...</i>

338
00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:10.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sakladık.

339
00:20:14.440 --> 00:20:15.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner nefes alır]

340
00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:21.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Biz Rüya'yla tanıştığımızda
daha vardı adam.

341
00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:25.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evli, büyük bir çocuğu var.

342
00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:30.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok eskiden tanıyor Rüya'yı.

343
00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:31.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dramatik müzik]

344
00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:35.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner nefes verir]

345
00:20:39.000 --> 00:20:40.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefes alır]

346
00:20:41.920 --> 00:20:44.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dönem dönem koptular.

347
00:20:46.520 --> 00:20:47.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[iç çeker]

348
00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:51.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her seferinde, bitti, dedim.

349
00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:53.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[hafif ağlamaklı]

350
00:20:53.480 --> 00:20:55.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu kâbus bitti.

351
00:20:55.560 --> 00:20:57.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[ağlamalı nefes] Sevindim.

352
00:21:00.840 --> 00:21:02.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[burun çeker]

353
00:21:02.440 --> 00:21:04.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sonra bir telefon... [ağlamaklı nefes]

354
00:21:06.600 --> 00:21:09.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Rüya boğazını temizler]
<i>-Her seferinde döndük başa.</i>

355
00:21:09.960 --> 00:21:11.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rüya nefes verir]

356
00:21:12.200 --> 00:21:13.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rüya boğazını temizler]

357
00:21:18.680 --> 00:21:19.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamam.

358
00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:33.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gergin nefesler]

359
00:21:35.040 --> 00:21:36.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Taner?

360
00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:39.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne... Ne yapıyorsun?

361
00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:41.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya Taner!

362
00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:44.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi, git şimdi!

363
00:21:50.320 --> 00:21:52.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[fonda dramatik müzik]

364
00:22:09.160 --> 00:22:10.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rüya?

365
00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:14.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Rüya?
-Konuşma benimle.

366
00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:16.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Ne olur bir dinle Rüya.
-Siktir git!

367
00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:17.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gitmek zorunda değilsin.

368
00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:19.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İhtiyacı var bana.

369
00:22:19.840 --> 00:22:23.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Adam gibi söyledim sana.
Hava kararacak zaten dedim.

370
00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:26.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Günümüzün içine sıçtın.
Ne vardı güzel güzel gitseydik evinimize?

371
00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:28.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yaptığın şeye bak. Çocuk gibi.

372
00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:29.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evimize gitseydik!

373
00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:32.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sonra arabana binseydin,
o şerefsizin yanına gitseydin.

374
00:22:32.840 --> 00:22:35.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kim sıçtı günün içine? O mu ben mi?

375
00:22:36.120 --> 00:22:37.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben sıçtım, ben.

376
00:22:37.360 --> 00:22:39.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefes nefese] Ben sıçtım, oldu mu? Ha?

377
00:22:40.080 --> 00:22:42.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben sıçtım be! Ben sıçtım!

378
00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:46.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Evliliğimizin içine sıçtım! Hayatımızın
içine sıçtım! Senin ağzına sıçtım!

379
00:22:46.520 --> 00:22:48.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben sıçtım be! Ben sıçtım!

380
00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:50.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[nefes nefese] Kaç defa söyledim sana!

381
00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:53.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben yanmışım, sen yanma, dedim.

382
00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:56.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[nefes nefese ağlayarak]
İstemiyorsan git dedim. Dinledin mi?

383
00:22:59.880 --> 00:23:01.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gel, yardım et. Bulalım şunu!

384
00:23:01.920 --> 00:23:04.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rüya nefes nefese]

385
00:23:04.280 --> 00:23:06.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Taner, yardım et, bulalım şu anahtarı.

386
00:23:08.360 --> 00:23:09.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[dramatik müzik]

387
00:23:13.800 --> 00:23:16.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Konuştum sabahlara kadar.

388
00:23:19.160 --> 00:23:22.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aklım eridi, içime aktı.

389
00:23:23.120 --> 00:23:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner burundan nefes verir]

390
00:23:26.080 --> 00:23:28.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sabrettim, vazgeçsin diye. [nefes alır]

391
00:23:35.760 --> 00:23:38.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[ağlamaklı nefes alır]

392
00:23:38.480 --> 00:23:40.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yaptıysam olmadı.

393
00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:42.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[ağlamaklı nefes]

394
00:23:44.720 --> 00:23:46.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kaçtı, gitti yine.

395
00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:50.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner nefes alır]

396
00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:51.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Çocuk" dedim. İstemedi.

397
00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:54.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gidelim buralardan, dedim.

398
00:23:55.200 --> 00:23:57.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Alayım seni, gidelim buralardan.

399
00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:00.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İstemedi.

400
00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:05.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[derin nefes] Ben karımın karısı oldum.

401
00:24:08.760 --> 00:24:11.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[burundan nefes] Aşık oldum ben karıma.

402
00:24:12.680 --> 00:24:14.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kocası olmadım.

403
00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:17.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İstemedi.

404
00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:21.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Taner derin nefes alır]

405
00:24:23.160 --> 00:24:25.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ondan konuşmadı demek benimle.

406
00:24:27.720 --> 00:24:29.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her seferinde sordum yaralarını.

407
00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:33.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her seferinde geçiştirdi.

408
00:24:35.640 --> 00:24:37.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benim kardeşim hasta belki, doğru.

409
00:24:39.280 --> 00:24:41.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Annem babam da... Anne baba işte öyle...

410
00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:44.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kolay değil, çocuğum üşütük diye...

411
00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:47.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...insan içine çıkmak. [nefes çeker]

412
00:24:47.560 --> 00:24:49.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anlamak gerekir onları.

413
00:24:49.560 --> 00:24:51.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen de haklısın.

